  "decision_conditions": [
    "REASON: The proposed first floor rear extension by virtue of its inappropriate design, scale and massing would form an over dominant and discordant feature when viewed from the private realm. The development would fail to respect its context and would create a visually harmful development which would have a detrimental visual impact on the character and appearance of the host building, its setting within the terrace and its surrounding conservation area setting. The proposal is therefore contrary to CS policy 9, policies D4, D11, D28 of the Islington Unitary Development Plan 2002, Islington's Urban Design Guidance 2006, Arlington Square conservation guidance note & section 12 of  the NPPF 2012."
